channel.description:
How to make people force headicon interface (like force skull) I'm making custom bounty hunter, and I'm atm trying to add portals, which will add on your head bounty hunter images, when clicked on them. (from rs back in 2007, bounty hunter crater)
any ideas?

item.title: Insta skull
item.dc:creator: @PvPXile PvPXile
item.description:
@PvPXile wrote:

Here’s my getPlayerSkull method.

public static int getPlayerSkull(Client plr) { int carrying = plr.getItems().getTotalNet(plr); return (carrying < 100000 ? BROWN_SKULL : carrying < 500000 && carrying > 100000 ? SILVER_SKULL : carrying < 1000000 && carrying > 500000 ? BLUE_SKULL : carrying < 5000000 && carrying > 1000000 ? GREEN_SKULL : carrying < 10000000 && carrying > 5000000 ? BLUE_SKULL : carrying > 10000000 || carrying < -1 ? RED_SKULL : -1); }

Please note this won’t work on its own.
